    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Race:</strong> Kobold&nbsp;<br /><strong>Replaced Trait(s):</strong> Crafty&nbsp;</p>\n<hr />\n<p>By observing the noises in underground  tunnels, you learned to uncannily mimic any voice or sound  you heard. Three times per day, you can attempt to trick  someone in this way by making a Bluff check against the  listener's Sense Motive check. You get a +2 circumstance  bonus on this check if you're in tunnels or other structures  where your voice can echo. This racial trait replaces crafty.</p>",
